==English==

=== Etymology ===
[[micro-]] and [[region]]

=== Noun ===
#A administrative system that is equivalent to a [[county]] or a [[prefecture]] and a [[department]].  It is used in [[Brazil]] as a third-level administration between [[state]] and [[micro-region]].

